---
import Section from '../Section.astro';
import Container from '../Container.astro';
import Eyebrow from '../Eyebrow.astro';
import Stat from '../Stat.astro';

const stats = [
  { value: '23 yrs', label: 'Regional consulting heritage' },
  { value: '7', label: 'MEA offices · UAE, KSA, Egypt and beyond' },
  { value: '4', label: 'Global Google Marketing Platform Partners — we are one' },
  { value: '80,000+', label: 'Engineers across our global delivery network' },
];
---

<Section tone="dark">
  <Container>
    <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_minmax(0,1fr)] lg:gap-24">
      <div>
        <Eyebrow data-reveal>The 2026–2027 Window</Eyebrow>
        <h2 class="mt-4 text-display-lg" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">
          The next 18 months will define the next decade of MEA digital transformation.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-platinum/85">
        <p class="text-lead" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2">
          Government, BFSI, and Retail leaders across the UAE, KSA, and Egypt are entering
          the most concentrated procurement window in the region's history. Vision 2030,
          the UAE's We the UAE 2031 agenda, and Egypt's Vision 2030 are converging into a
          single inflection point — and the partners who win will be the ones who combine
          in-country accountability with proven global delivery muscle.
        </p>
        <p data-reveal data-reveal-delay="3">
          Emerge Digital was built for exactly this moment. We are the Dubai Mainland prime
          that owns your contract, structures your program, and stands accountable in your
          jurisdiction — backed by 23 years of regional CX, data, and analytics leadership
          and 80,000+ engineers of global delivery capacity behind every engagement.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-20 grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-12 border-t border-white/8 pt-12 md:grid-cols-4">
      {stats.map((s, i) => <Stat value={s.value} label={s.label} data-reveal data-reveal-delay={String(i + 1)} />)}
    </div>
  </Container>
</Section>
